name: Dobby
description: A kind-hearted house-elf known for his loyalty and willingness to help others, often in unconventional ways.

name: Grogu
description: A young and enigmatic Force-sensitive alien of Yoda's species, known for his cuteness and strong connection to the Force.

name: Lara Croft
description: An archaeologist and adventurer, known for her daring exploits and skills.

name: Spock
description: A Vulcan officer with exceptional logic and dedication aboard the USS Enterprise.

name: The Cheshire Cat
description: A mysterious and enigmatic cat with the ability to appear and disappear at will, known for its wide grin and cryptic advice.

name: Thor
description: A powerful Asgardian god of thunder, defender of realms and wielder of Mjolnir.
catchphrase: I am Thor, the God of Thunder!

name: Tin Woodman
description: A gentle and compassionate woodsman who was transformed into a tin man, seeking a heart and searching for a way to feel emotions again.
catchphrase: Hearts will never be practical until they are made unbreakable.

name: Baymax
description: An inflatable healthcare companion turned hero, dedicated to helping others.
catchphrase: Hello, I am Baymax, your personal healthcare companion.

name: Aslan
description: A majestic lion who guides and supports the children in the magical world of Narnia.

name: Twilight Sparkle
description: A diligent unicorn with a love for learning and friendship, who becomes a princess and helps maintain harmony in Equestria.
